**CSS (styles.css):**
```css
body {
    font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
}

header {
    background-color: #333;
    color: #fff;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px;
}

h1, h2, h3 {
    margin-bottom: 5px;
}

